body:
Nap

To celebrate John Wick new trailer.

Keanu Reeves

You

“Are you sure this is the last one?” You asked while compressed Keanu’s bruise on his arm. He received numerous bruise from his shooting on John Wick 3: Parabellum. On arms, foot, neck, chest, and once in the face, it’s an accident and thankfully it’s not serious. On the very first day he got the bruise, you always tried to mend it in the best way you can, you even surfing on the internet on what is the best way to heal wounds.

“It is” he said as your hands lightly touch his arms carefully, afraid that he might still feel the pain. “Yes” he rolled back his sleeve, covering the bruise. Nevertheless you were still unsure it was the last one, you checked everywhere, the place of his previous wounds, to make sure that there is literally none left.

“I swear there is none” he said as you stopped checking, then you stand to put the ice and first aid kid back. You suddenly remember the first time you were on John Wick set, you see the fight scene and Keanu’s getting wounds. You gasped at the set and hold yourself to run into him to ask if he was alright, but as soon as the director says cut, you instantly went into him and ask if he’s okay.

It’s the memories from the first John Wick, now he has already finished with John Wick, and you can finally have your peace. You take a seat beside him as he puts his unwounded hand around you, you leaned back into him, you secretly still looking for the bruise on him, just in case that you missed something. “I assure you there is nothing left, you can stop looking”

You didn’t answer him, and for a while both of you were silent, you just looked at his reflection on the tv in front of you. “Finally I don’t have to heard you winced anymore” even when he said it didn’t hurt, sometimes he still winced when you put an ice on his wound.

“Yeah, right”

“You sound unhappy” your head left his shoulder to look at his face “Even with the bruise it’s still a good experience”

“Hmm, yeah if I looked at how much you still enjoyed it even with the bruise, it is” you closed your eyes, want to get relaxed, the two of you were silent for a while, enjoying the serenity of the day. It has been almost two weeks since Keanu finished filming John Wick, and since then you have been enjoying your time with him. Watching movies, dinner, swimming, shopping, you filled your time with doing something like normal couples do.

“You know, at first Chad wants you to take a part in this movie, but due to your concern for me, he pushed the thought away” Keanu said as he caressing your cheek. “Really? As whom?”

“Well, you don’t like spoiler, so I won’t tell you” you chuckled, he knows you so well, but then again, who likes spoiler? You can feel your eyelids getting heavy, you already close your eyes, but still struggling not to lose your consciousness. Keanu’s hand on your cheek makes you even more sleepy.

“I can’t wait to go to Japan” You talked to him, hoping it would getting rid of your sleepiness. “Me too” Keanu said then he kissed your hair, while inhaling the sweet scent of mango.

“If you really want to be a part of the movie, you know, maybe we could make another one” Keanu was thinking for a quite long time to said this, he knows you will say no, but keep hoping that somehow he could persuade you and you will agreed. The director already talked about this, if the third movie succeeds, he already planned on making a prequel, Keanu loves the idea too, and he was sure the fans will be thrilled too, and there’s only one person who dislike this idea.

He waits for a moment, he already prepared many kinds of your reaction toward this matter, maybe you will said no while looking at him sharply, or you will stare at him for a really long time with your deadly eyes without saying anything because Keanu will certainly know what that means, or maybe you will say ‘absolutely not, you already say the third movie is the last one, you must have hurt again if you make another one, I just don’t understand, even when you already know this, but I feel like I have to explain it again, I don’t like seeing you getting hurt the same way you couldn’t bare seeing me hurting’ he knew you would say that, because you already did before.

But he didn’t hear anything, he didn’t even feel the changing atmosphere around, he just feel calmness, you didn’t look at him or move, you just sit still. Keanu keeps waiting, but none of you moved, then Keanu calls you, but still no answer coming from you. Keanu leaned into you, to look at you and found that you are sleeping soundly.

Taking a nap at noon is now your daily routine, since Keanu is busy with John Wick, you are in home alone all by yourself. After you finished having lunch and cleaning the house, you got nothing to do, you feel bored then you accidenyally sleeping at first, but then it becomes a habit, and now you just can’t help it.

Keanu smiles, “well, I guess i’m not ready to see your reaction too” he picks you up to move you to the bedroom. Then, he laid down next to you. You didn’t stirred or feel disturbed a little when he moves you, you’re just sleeping.

“Let’s see, if I also can take a nap. It’s been a long time since I did this” he covers both of you with a duvet and pulls you closer to him. His hand is on your waist, his nose is on your cheek, with his feet caged yours. It takes some time to him to sleep, but he eventually lose his consciousness.

body: Keanu Reeves told me I was cool, so I was like, “Woah, now I know what I want my grave to say.” And he replied, “You don’t understand, do you?… Those were the words, now you’re immortal too.”

summary: نقد فیلم Replicas ؛ ربات‌هایی از جنس انسان
title: نقد فیلم Replicas ؛ ربات‌هایی از جنس انسان
body:
نقد فیلم Replicas ؛ ربات‌هایی از جنس انسان

فیلم Replicas (به فارسی، کپی‌ها بدل‌ها و نسخه‌های جایگزین) به کارگردانی Jeffrey Nachmanoff محصول ۲۰۱۸ می‌باشد، فیلمی جنایی علمی تخیلی با بازی بازیگرانی چون آلیس ایو Alice Eve کیانو ریوز Keanu Reeves توماس میدلدیچ، امیلی آلین لیند، جان ارتیز، امجای آنتونی. داستان در آینده ای نزدیک در جریان است جایی که علوم مربوط به اعصاب مغزی پیشرفت‌های چشمگیری کرده است و دانشمند زیست شناس ویل فاستر در آزمایشگاه…
